    <div id="sidr">
    <h1 class="droid">NewsMash is an application that helps users get to the news they want quickly. Newsmash gets news from all across the web programaatically, using content from the New York Times, The Guardian, Twitter and Reddit. Users are thus always kept updated with the latest stories, even as they are breaking. NewsMash is delivered over a CDN and ensures that the load times are minimal.  In addition, the NewsMash Bot (fully open source) is constantly sniffing for news stories. This is a project that is made possible thanks to a lot of existing services. Fork NewsMash on Github if you want to help the news bot become better!
    </h2>
    </div>
